'''格伦·爱德华·麥克达菲'''（{{lang-en|'''Glenn Edward McDuffie'''}}，{{bd|1927年|5月31日|2014年|3月9日|catIdx=McDuffie}}），美军二战水手，因[[艾尔弗雷德·艾森斯塔特|艾尔弗雷德·艾森斯塔特]]的照片《[[胜利之吻|胜利之吻]]》闻名于世<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/sailor-wwii-kiss-photo-dies-article-1.1721784|title=Glenn Edward McDuffie, who long claimed to be sailor in iconic Times Square ‘kiss’ photo at end of WWII, dies|publisher=[[New_York_Daily_News|New York Daily News]].com|accessdate=March 15, 2014|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208083901/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/sailor-wwii-kiss-photo-dies-article-1.1721784|dead-url=no}}</ref>。因二战结束，他当时在时代广场亲吻护士[[伊迪丝·夏安|伊迪丝·夏安]]，成为历史上著名的时刻。 

麥克达菲出生于[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]][[坎纳波利斯|坎纳波利斯]]，之后参加美国海军。二战后，他就职于[[美国邮政局|美国邮政局]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ajc.com/news/news/national/kissing-sailor-famous-wwii-photograph-dies/nfDT3/|title='Kissing sailor' from famous WWII photograph dies|publisher=[[Atlanta_Journal-Constitution|Atlanta Journal-Constitution]]|accessdate=March 15, 2014|archive-date=2014-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140315155838/http://www.ajc.com/news/news/national/kissing-sailor-famous-wwii-photograph-dies/nfDT3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年3月9日，他在因心脏病死于[[达拉斯|达拉斯]]，享年86岁<ref>[http://www.apdnews.com/news/77028.html 经典照片《胜利之吻》男主角离世] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140318095632/http://www.apdnews.com/news/77028.html |date=2014-03-18 }}，亚太日报，2014年3月18日</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/glenn-mcduffie-man-known-as-kissing-sailor-in-wwii-era-photo-dead-at-86-1.2573355|title=Glenn McDuffie, man known as kissing sailor in WWII-era photo, dead at 86|publisher=[[CBC|CBC News]].com|accessdate=March 15, 2014|archive-date=2014-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140315034853/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/glenn-mcduffie-man-known-as-kissing-sailor-in-wwii-era-photo-dead-at-86-1.2573355|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

